      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint, showroom-quality condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and absolutely no scratches, chips, or dents. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, retaining its original factory scent and showing no signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did when it first left the dealership, offering a smooth and powerful driving experience that reflects its low-mileage, high-standard maintenance history.",
