    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable set of wheels that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in great shape, runs super smoothly, and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It's perfect for someone who wants a solid, dependable ride that still looks great in the driveway. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 33500.0,
