      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. The chassis remains composed thanks to upgraded Bilstein dampers and a reinforced rear subframe\u2014a critical preventive measure already addressed. With a factory limited-slip differential and refreshed bushings, the turn-in is sharp and communicative. The VANOS system has been professionally serviced, ensuring the variable valve timing operates within factory spec. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, making this a driver-focused example ready for the canyon roads.",
